RenderableGraph - Interface in renderGraph
This is the interface that is to be implemented by a class representing a graph to be rendered by RenderGraph.

renderGraph - package renderGraph
This package offers functionality to render graphs to png files in a very comfortable but admittedly not very customizable way.
RenderGraph - Class in renderGraph
This Class offers two methods for rendering a graph either as a run-of-the-mill graph or as a bipartite graph.
